      <h1>Silicon <br/>Milkroundabout</h1>
      <h3>Branding, design, strategy &amp; copywriting</h3>
      <ul class="bullets push-top-half t-center">
        <li>Helped refine recurring processes to reduce design production time by half</li>
        <li>Redesigned wayfinding and floorplans to improve navigation of events</li>
        <li>Rewrote and rebuilt entire MailChimp marketing campaign</li>
